"6  Anaheim chiles","1 tablespoon peanut oil","3  chicken leg quarters, skinned (about 1 3/4 pounds)","1 3/4 cups chopped onion","4  garlic cloves, minced","4 cups fat-free, less-sodium chicken broth","2 cups water, divided","1 1/2 teaspoons ground cumin","1  (15.5-ounce) can cannellini beans (such as Goya) or other white beans, rinsed and drained","3 tablespoons all-purpose flour","1 teaspoon salt","3 tablespoons reduced-fat sour cream","6  lime slices"